{"id":741555,"date":[{"year":1987,"month":1,"day":31}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"周末","column":"娱乐厅","genre":"","count":"201","ytitle":"","mtitle":"上期娱乐厅答案","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"故事谜谜底，第一条是云，第二条是“比上不足，比下有余”。(注:“运动会”三字都有“云”。“上”指爬山，“下”指下期)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含“春”谜谜底:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风得意马蹄疾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(孟郊《登科后》)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春作伴好还乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(杜甫《闻官军收河南河北》)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一树春风万千枝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(白居易《杨柳枝词》)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾若伤春不忍听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(李商隐《流莺》)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还似洞庭春水色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(温庭筠《咸阳值雨》)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我言秋月胜春朝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(杨巨源《城东早春》)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力家清景在新春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(刘禹锡《秋词二首》)"}]}